Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Under Kamala, there will be no car industry, no steel industry, no significant manufacturing of any kind—and we will be at risk of military defeat...and I am not going to allow Japan to buy U.S. Steel, 70 years ago the greatest company on earth!
